better.

160
00:06:44,020 --> 00:06:45,470
They just believe it would make it harder

161
00:06:45,470 --> 00:06:47,270
for Trump to get things done.

162
00:06:47,270 --> 00:06:51,060
They’re right, but not in the way that matters
most to them.

163
00:06:51,060 --> 00:06:53,720
Because while Trump would have to fight a
Democratic Congress

164
00:06:53,720 --> 00:06:55,889
