as a presidential candidate,

174
00:07:19,400 --> 00:07:20,979
like other past candidates,

175
00:07:20,979 --> 00:07:23,990
but then soften his stance when he became
the president,

176
00:07:23,990 --> 00:07:25,770
like other past presidents.

177
00:07:25,770 --> 00:07:28,210
And at first, it looked like that might happen.

178
00:07:28,210 --> 00:07:31,070
But now it’s pretty clear that the Trump
administration

179
00:07:31,070 --> 00:07:33,280
is changing the US approach to China.

180
00:07:33,280 --> 00:07:37,080
